11 BE IT ENACTED BY THE PEOPLE OF THE STATE OF OKLAHOMA:
12 SECTION 1. REPEALER 17 O.S. 2021, Section 802.3, as last
13 amended by Section 2, Chapter 31, O.S.L. 2024 (17 O.S. Supp. 2025,
14 Section 802.3) is hereby repealed.
15 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2026.
